	<div style="text-align:right;">
		IZIDORO, Andressa Moretti<sup>1</sup>; MORAES, Thyago Proença de<sup>2</sup>; PECOITS FILHO, Roberto<sup>3</sup>; CAMPOS, Ludimila Guedim de<sup>4</sup>		<BR>
